<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Rhian Sugden celebrated her 34th birthday in style on Friday night. </p>

<p>The former glamour model cut a glamorous figure as she headed out for dinner with her husband Oliver Mellor, 39, and friends at The Ivy in Manchester.</p>

<p>Rhian looked lovely in a lilac polka dot minidress which made the most of her tanned legs.  </p>

<p>Birthday girl: Rhian Sugden celebrated her 34th birthday in style on Friday night</p>

<p>The minidress cinched in Rhian's slender waist and featured pleated detailing on the skirt. </p>

<p>She added a boost to her height with nude Louboutin stilettos and complemented her birthday outfit with a metallic gold shoulder bag. </p>

<p>Rhian amped up the glamour by styling her hair in voluminous curls and accentuated her bronzed complexion with a full face of make-up.  </p>

<p>Gorgeous: The former glamour model cut a glamorous figure as she headed out for dinner with her husband Oliver Mellor, 39, and friends at The Ivy in Manchester</p>

<p>Leggy display: Rhian looked lovely in a lilac polka dot minidress which made the most of her tanned legs, while Oliver cut a dapper figure in a striped shirt, leather jacket and jeans</p>

<p>Oliver, meanwhile, cut a dapper figure in a striped shirt, leather jacket and jeans. </p>

<p>The couple appeared in the throes of love as they headed into the restaurant.  </p>

<p>Earlier this month, Rhian revealed she put on a half a stone during lockdown but is embracing her new curves. </p>

<p>She wrote on Instagram: 'Has anyone else packed on a few pounds in lockdown? I’ve put on over half a stone and can’t for the life of me get motivated to go to the gym.  </p>

<p>'But putting my gym gear on is a step in the right direction right?</p>

<p>'I wish I was one of those people that enjoys working out and running etc... I just like eating and laying down too much.' </p>

<p>The glamour model is married to former Coronation Street actor Oliver and the couple have been enduring gruelling IVF for 20 months.    </p>

<p>After discovering that she wouldn’t be able to conceive naturally,  they went through two rounds of IVF and are planning their third.</p>

<p>Throughout the process, experts recommended she stopped using all cosmetic products that contain hash chemicals or additives, which is when she decided to go tan-free for over 12 months.   </p>

